OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy evening with a few light
OL,7,Fshowers around. Showers will tend to
OL,8,Fdie out overnight with some clear
OL,9,Fspells developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FDry through the morning with
OL,12,Fgood sunny spells. Turning cloudy with
OL,13,Fsome showers spreading east through
OL,14,Fthe late afternoon and evening.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,17,Fmixture of sunshine and showers on
OL,18,FTuesday and Wednesday. Longer spells
OL,19,Fof rain possible on Thursday. Feeling
OL,20,Frather cool for the time of year.
